67
00:04:07,820 --> 00:04:08,999
Hurry up, don't make her wait.

68
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,940
Take the call. It's okay.

69
00:04:11,700 --> 00:04:13,239
Hello, Sister Wenwen.

70
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:14,879
 Hello, Xiaoning, are you busy? 

71
