I have something to talk to you about.

73
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:20,239
How about we have lunch together during your lunch break?

74
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:21,180
 My treat. 

75
00:04:21,180 --> 00:04:24,420
Sure. I'll bring you the design proposal then.

76
00:04:24,420 --> 00:04:27,099
Okay. I'll send you the address in a bit.

77
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,560
See you at noon.

78
